            . I am a fancy trimming manufacturer, and live in <placeName id="t18250915-328-crimeloc1772">Leadenhall-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18250915-328-crimeloc1772" type="placeName" value="Leadenhall-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18250915-328-crimeloc1772" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-328-off1770 t18250915-328-crimeloc1772"></join>. On the morning of the 12th of September, while I was at breakfast, I saw the prisoner go out of my shop, with a paper parcel under his arm, wrapped up in an old newspaper - I followed him immediately, and brought him back with it; this is the parcel - it is the property of Mr. John Danford. I had seen it on the counter about ten minutes before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18250915-328-person1654">
                  JOHN 
                  OVENDON
