                     <interp inst="t18250915-328-person1654" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the officer. Mr. Danford gave me these bell-pulls. I took the prisoner into custody.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. A man came up to me, and said he would give me 2 d. to go and get the parcel off the counter, and if any body said any thing to me to say it was my brother's; I went - this gentleman came out, and took me. The man who sent me went away.</p>
